CSS css

### 

- Less css
- SassStylus 
- Sass
  ```
  .header
    background-color:red
  ```
- Less & SCSS
  ```
  .header {
    background-color:red;
  }
  ```
- Stylus
  ```
  .header
    background-color:red
  ```

### 

- , Sass  Stylus 
- less
  ```
  .header {
    &.title {
      color: red;
    }
  }
  ```

### 

-  CSS CSS
- Sass
  ```
  $bg: #ccc;

  .header 
    background-color:$bg;
  ```
- Less
  ```
  @bg: #ccc;

  header {
    background-color: @bg;
  }
  ```
- Stylus
  ```
  bg = #ccc

  header
    background-color: bg
  ```

### @import

- Sass  url() 
  ```
  $public: public;

  @import url(styles.#{$public}.css);
  ```
- Less
  ```
  @public: public;

  @import "styles.@{public}.css";
  ```
- Stylus 
  ```
  public = "public"

  @import "styles." + public + ".css"
  ```


### (Mixins)

- : 
- Sass
  ```
  @mixin product-public-text {
    font: {
      size: 20px;
      weight: 600;
      family: PingFangSC;
    }
    color: rgba(72,72,72,1);
  }
  .product-header-title {
    @include product-public-text;
    padding: 10px;
  }
  ```

- Less
  ```
  .product-public-font-weight {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .product-public-font(@color: red) {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: @color;
  }

  .product-header-title{
    .product-public-font-weight;
    .product-public-font(red);
  }
  ```

### 

- Sass
  ```
  .header {
    background-color: red;
  }
  .main.active {
    @extend .header;
  }
  ```

- less
  ```
  .header {
    background-color: red;
  }
  .main {
    &:extend(.header);
  }
  ```

- Stylus,Scss
  ```
  .header
    background-color: red;

  .main
    @extend .header
  ```

